                     <interp inst="t18221204-98-off517" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221204-98-off517" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously falsely and making and forging a certain order for payment of 6 l. 9 s., with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18221204-98-victim930" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Birt
                        <interp inst="t18221204-98-victim930" type="surname" value="Birt"></interp>
